{"tid":338171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚政總外舉行集會反「割地兩檢」 歡迎通宵留守","createTime":"2017-07-28T03:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T09:33:41.000Z","uid":48093,"like":6,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66b96e151cda9a2346ce39afef8fb8b079b6d2b7","tid":338171,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T03:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170728/large/1501211463_b1d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170728%2Flarge%2F1501211463_b1d2.jpg&h=5f86ec62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府決定將廣深港高鐵香港段西九總站劃出「內地口岸區」，以作一地兩檢，被炮轟是割地自閹。立法會議員毛孟靜及張超雄、新民主同盟范國威等18人一同發起今晚8時於金鐘政府總部連儂牆外舉行「反對『割地兩檢』民眾集會」，以向政府表達對一地兩檢的不滿。活動預計在晚上10時結束，發起人表明歡迎參與者在集會後通宵留守。"},{"pid":"dbfdd8e510b9076c0668cf0aae865f624a9b78fd","tid":338171,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T03:33:42.000Z","msg":"和平理性非暴力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77a2ab0c050c27bc0a7b96c0421df168499952c","tid":338171,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T03:38:40.000Z","msg":"乜唔係話唔搞和理非集會咩？<br />\n<br />\n乜唔係去集會你地又話人左膠啦？"},{"pid":"63cae3ec44af02d98f5f723d9ac6930479d139e8","tid":338171,"uid":15711,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T03:41:16.000Z","msg":"拿，有人理啦，有人搞搞集會啦，連登仔又話人唱今天我又唔敢去<br />\n<br />\n但就怨婦咁話無人理 無人理 無人理"},{"pid":"da118f25a4f6ce7cc36d36cee26003e90f4a5f26","tid":338171,"uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T03:45:45.000Z","msg":"有用咩！？<br />\n泛民總辭就考慮去<br />\n否則 不了"},{"pid":"ae320c91a8fa9cb7eecfdd0c4da68e0be0787729","tid":338171,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite